    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu </p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 6</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 6</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 18 | <b>Successes:</b> 2</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 7 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 19</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> S</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You touch a surface directly connected to the target area and send a volatile wave of sound towards it, havarea.<br><br>Close; Area: 10 ft. Burst; Duration: Instant *; Save: Reing an effect based on the type of surface in the targeted<br><br>Hard Ground: The wave sends debris flying in all directions; dealing 2d6 bludgeoning and 2d6 slashing damage which can be halved with a Reflex save. A single square inside the area is treated as though it had caltrops spread over it until it is repaired (the surface takes triple damage from this technique).<br><br>Soft Ground: A wave of mud or a cloud of sand and/or dirt is sent flying up, leaving all creatures @Condition[blind]{blinded} for 1d4 unless they succeed at a Fortitude save.</p>\n\n\n\n",
